title: Dialogue 1/6
author: The Transcriber
pages: Rune: Hey, did you catch that bizarre talk in the void?
Skye: Yeah, those voices were kinda weaving through big ideas.
Rune: Yeah! It was deep, yet muddled.
Skye: Maybe they were diving into dreams and beyond?
Rune: Dreams? I thought it was more about creation itself.
Skye: Could be both. Felt like echoes through time.
